02830                                         input1 += inputOffset;
02831                                         input2 += inputOffset;
02832                                         input3 += inputOffset;
02833                                         output0 += outputOffset;
02834                                         output1 += outputOffset;
02835                                         output2 += outputOffset;
02836                                         output3 += outputOffset;
02837                                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02838                                         output4 += outputOffset;
02839                                         #endif
02840                                         if ((*input0 ^ ein_cache[0]) || (*input1 ^ ein_cache[1]) || (*input2 ^ ein_cache[2]) || (*input3 ^ ein_cache[3]))
02841                                         {
02842                                                 break;
02843                                         }
02844                                         *output0 = output0[-outputOffset];
02845                                         *output1 = output1[-outputOffset];
02846                                         *output2 = output2[-outputOffset];
02847                                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02848                                         *output3 = output3[-outputOffset];
02849                                         *output4 &= Mask;
02850                                         #else
02851                                         *output3 &= Mask;
02852                                         #endif
02853                                 }
02854                         }
02855                         else
02856                         {
02857                                 #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02858                                 *output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02859                                 #else
02860                                 *output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02861                                 #endif
02862                                 while (--i)
02863                                 {                                                               /*U_TO_U*/
02864                                         input0 += inputOffset;
02865                                         input1 += inputOffset;
02866                                         input2 += inputOffset;
02867                                         input3 += inputOffset;
02868                                         input4 += inputOffset;
02869 
02870                                         output0 += outputOffset;
02871                                         output1 += outputOffset;
02872                                         output2 += outputOffset;
02873                                         output3 += outputOffset;
02874                                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02875                                         output4 += outputOffset;
02876                                         #endif
02877                                         if ((*input0 ^ ein_cache[0]) || (*input1 ^ ein_cache[1]) || (*input2 ^ ein_cache[2]) || (*input3 ^ ein_cache[3]))
02878                                         {
02879                                                 break;
02880                                         }
02881                                         *output0 = output0[-outputOffset];
02882                                         *output1 = output1[-outputOffset];
02883                                         *output2 = output2[-outputOffset];
02884                                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02885                                         *output3 = output3[-outputOffset];
02886                                         *output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02887                                         #else
02888                                         *output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE)*input4;
02889                                         #endif
02890                                 }
02891                         }
02892                 }
02893                 if (--LineCount)
02894                 {
02895                         j++;
02896                         input0 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[0] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02897                         input1 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[1] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02898                         input2 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[2] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02899                         input3 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[3] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02900                         input4 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->inputData[4] + j * calcParam->cmInputBytesPerLine);
02901 
02902                         output0 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[0] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02903                         output1 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[1] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02904                         output2 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[2] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02905                         output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[3] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02906                         #if LH_DATA_OUT_COUNT_4
02907                         output4 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)((LH_UINT8 *)calcParam->outputData[4] + j * calcParam->cmOutputBytesPerLine);
02908                         #endif
02909                 }
02910         }
02911         LH_END_PROC(LH_CALC_PROC_NAME)
02912         return 0;
02913 }
02914 #else
02915 {
02916 
02917         LH_UINT32 ein_regb;
02918         LH_UINT32 ein_regg;
02919         LH_UINT32 ein_regr;
02920         LH_DATA_IN_TYPE ein_cache[3];

02930         LH_DATA_IN_TYPE * input1 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)calcParam->inputData[1];
02931         LH_DATA_IN_TYPE * input2 = (LH_DATA_IN_TYPE *)calcParam->inputData[2];

02936         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE * output2 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)calcParam->outputData[2];
02937         LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE * output3 = (LH_DATA_OUT_TYPE *)calcParam->outputData[3];

02950

02953         #else

02955         #endif

02970                 LineCount = 1;

02978         {
